{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act45side", "eventName": "無憂夢囈", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "SS-1", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "花格窗邊的夢想", "storyInfo": "除了祥子，Ave{@nbs}Mujica的成員們都深陷於夢境中。祥子與夢城堡的“主人”莫菲絲達成賭約，前往每個成員的夢境中嘗試喚醒她們。然而，祥子一進入若麥的夢境，就被若麥鋪天蓋地的廣告所震驚。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness02_intro", "key": "$darkness02_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>童話書裡說，在維多利亞的某處矗立著一座只有孩子才能看見的城堡。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>城堡裡住著幾位善良的仙女，她們會定期舉辦宴會招待孩子們，並用美夢一一實現他們的願望。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>但如果想細問“夢城堡”到底是什麼模樣，卻沒有一個孩子能回答得出來。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>精心創造的美夢，從孩子們離開夢境的那一刻起，就在不斷地被淡忘。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>美夢不斷被塑造，然後又不斷被遺忘。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>重複塑造，重複遺忘。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>這一切對於善良而忙碌的仙女們來說，是不是有點不太公平？</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>“是的，莫菲絲。”</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "65_g2_dreamcastlehall", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歡迎來到夢城堡，我是這裡的現任主人，莫菲絲。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夢城堡……的主人……不對，你做了什麼？！", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和你夢裡演的一樣啊？只不過是讓你們做了一個夢罷了。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉——不過你的夢實在太無趣了，都是一些無聊的東西。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#17$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#16$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）還有那兩個……討厭的傢伙。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#16$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你認識愛麗絲……還有貝娜？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不熟。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#17$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她們不是夢裡的角色，是真實存在的人？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我倒希望她們只存在於夢裡。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#17$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可以不要一直提那兩個傢伙嗎？", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#9$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在和我說話欸！現在我才是這裡的主人！", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#10$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快點讓我離開這裡。", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那不可能。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#17$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最近都沒什麼孩子來夢城堡了，我怎麼可能隨便放你走？", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#15$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡爾頓們又不能說話，沃爾夫只有一個，而且現在話都說不清楚。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#15$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1937_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_yingying_ked_2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（失落的哼唧聲）", "name": "卡爾頓們"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1937_1#5$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1938_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱、抱歉。", "name": "沃爾夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1938_1#2$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是因為自己太無聊了，所以才把我關在這個城堡裡的嗎？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要說得好像我來者不拒一樣。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的經歷都很有趣——記憶裡的那些經歷還有那些陌生的場景，我反覆研究了很多遍呢。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你偷看了我的記憶？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個傢伙沒有和你說過嗎？瞭解孩子們的過去，也是塑造夢境很重要的一部分。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你確實是個例外……", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明明經歷了那麼多無法忘卻的事情，頭腦卻還是一如既往地清醒。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了彌補這個小小的遺憾，我願意為你重新塑造一個美夢。正好我們現在面對面，你可以跟我說一下——", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沉溺在夢境和過往的痛苦中，都是懦弱的表現。", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵，你還真是嘴硬！", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果按照你說的，無法面對現實的人全都是懦夫的話……", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那這樣的人，真的很多呢。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snapping", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "65_i02_2", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_craneworking", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帷幕漸漸拉開，座椅從台下緩緩升起。"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而座椅上坐著的，是祥子再熟悉不過的人。"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "初華……睦？", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祐天寺……還有八幡？", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……大家怎麼都睡著了？", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "周圍的一切猶如舞台布景。"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沉睡的少女們，就是巨大布景中安眠的人偶。"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無聲，無息。"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子一遍遍地嘗試喚醒自己的同伴，卻仍無濟於事。"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別白費力氣了，沒用的。", "name": "莫菲絲"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "65_i02_1", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我對自己的能力還是很有信心的。她們正沉浸在自己的美夢裡，你叫不醒她們的。", "name": "莫菲絲"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我為你們創造的夢境裡有什麼不好？", "name": "莫菲絲"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅德島的朋友們都相信你，這樣不好嗎？沒有任何你不想看到的別離，你也不用隱藏自己。", "name": "莫菲絲"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看看她們，難道你要說她們都是懦夫嗎？", "name": "莫菲絲"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然我有辦法從你的夢中醒來，她們也一定可以……", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_strngspllstght", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "s"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "s", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "突然間，祥子感到幾股巨大的力量拉住自己，等她反應過來時，她的四肢已經被絲線牢牢綑綁。"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無法控制身體的緊張感瞬間侵占了她的思維，她努力地想讓自己保持冷靜。"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而，緊繃的絲線將她身上一切微弱的抖動毫無保留地放大。"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這個嘴硬的傢伙，就不能承認夢境是美好的嗎！", "name": "莫菲絲"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你……", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子努力想辦法讓自己的呼吸變得平順。"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你……似乎對自己的能力很有自信。", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許在我來到這裡之前，從來沒有人打破過你的夢境。", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然！我本來就是這個城堡裡最擅長造夢的仙女。", "name": "莫菲絲"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的甦醒只不過是一個意外，再來一次肯定就沒問題了！", "name": "莫菲絲"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子清楚地看到，莫菲絲說出最後那幾個字時，明明是咬牙切齒的表情，但轉眼間又變得無比天真燦爛。"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……豐川祥子，對吧？", "name": "莫菲絲"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然你這麼有自信，那我就跟你打個賭！", "name": "莫菲絲"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……打賭？", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯！絕對公平的打賭喔！", "name": "莫菲絲"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眼前的對手越是露出孩童般的微笑，就越顯得無比危險。"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，很簡單！", "name": "莫菲絲"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然那孩子繞著舞台轉著圈，但祥子很清楚她肯定一直在盯著自己。並且，黑暗中還有無數雙眼睛也在緊盯著自己。"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會邀請你進入她們每一個人的夢境，讓你有機會喚醒她們。", "name": "莫菲絲"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可以認識她們、瞭解她們，看看她們到底在夢境中過著怎樣的生活。如果你能讓她們像你一樣醒來，我就讓你們離開。", "name": "莫菲絲"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你失敗了，那她們就要永遠留在夢境裡！", "name": "莫菲絲"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我會把她們都叫醒的。", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Ave{@nbs}Mujica少了任何一個人，我都不會離開。", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她們每個人都是我挑選出來的、最好的成員。我不會讓她們任何一個人受你的擺布。", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，那就不一定囉。如果你失敗了，你也要重新進入我為你創造的夢境。", "name": "莫菲絲"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這次你一定不會再醒過來的。我會讓你忘記以前的一切痛苦，自願活在裡面。", "name": "莫菲絲"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼樣？還是說，你想收回之前說的那些話了？", "name": "莫菲絲"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算我現在拒絕，你也不可能放我走吧？", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈！你很聰明嘛！", "name": "莫菲絲"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "豐川祥子，我很期待你在她們的夢境裡，露出絕望又無助的表情。", "name": "莫菲絲"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會向你證明——你逃不掉的。", "name": "莫菲絲"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_strngspllmgc", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "type": "cg", "from": 0.0, "to": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 0.1, "type": "bg", "from": 0.0, "to": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫菲絲手指輕動，祥子的視線頓時變得模糊不清。"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔——！", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.2}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "65_g8_interviewstage", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.2}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "65_i04", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.2}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "65_i07_2", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_light", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_tinnitus", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "五顏六色、變異扭曲的光影湧入祥子的腦海中。"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "舞台下喧鬧歡呼的人群。"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雨夜中的一抹黑影。"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "坐在椅子上的孤獨少女。"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有無數個無法分清的人影。"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "享受我為你們創造的美夢吧——", "name": "莫菲絲"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_dream_change", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_blackmask", "layer": 2.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 0.1, "type": "bg", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_lmstreet_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_traffic_amb", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "川流不息的車陣、高聳入雲的建築還有無處不在的霓虹招牌。"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從夢境裡出來了？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不對……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nightoflongmen_intro", "key": "$nightoflongmen_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛出鍋的新鮮鱗丸哦——快來看看！", "name": "賣力的商販"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_304_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快點快點，後面還有很多人在等！活動快開始了啊！", "name": "匆忙的行人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_304_1#1$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_033", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你好！包裹到囉——人不在家？請問我可以放在門口嗎？", "name": "幹練的快遞員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_033"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現代的建築、動物的耳朵……這裡到底是哪裡？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Dialog"